structure.unit: A CABINET FOR HEALTH AND FAMILY SERVICES

law.catch_line: Sections and amendments to be known as "Boni Frederick Bill."
law.text: In honor of Boni Frederick who lost her life in the performance of her official duties, KRS 194A.560, 194A.562, 194A.564, 194A.566, and 605.170, and the amendments made to KRS 194A.065 in 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 140, shall be known as the "Boni Frederick Bill."
law.history: Created 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 140, sec. 1, effective April 5, 2007.
